cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DB

The paper discusses the challenges faced by organizations in complying with the GDPR, which is a regulation related to data protection and privacy. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.DB (Databases).
